title: AIDinoGame
author: AIDinoGame
content: There is no need to wait for a quantum computer. I used AI to crack the Bitcoin wallet. The basic efficiency of cracking increased by 83.33%. In the future, if AI generates wisdom, the "encryption" of the cryptocurrency wallet will be transparent to AI.I use AI to crack Bitcoin wallet, I call it "AI Dino Game", if anyone is interested, I will publish my cracking process and method. This is a fun game, once you start playing, you won't stop.

comments.author: Oshosondy
comments.body: Quote from: AIDinoGame on April 26, 2024, 09:22:24 AMI use AI to crack Bitcoin walletYou do not have to come to this forum to post rubbish. The device needed to brute force bitcoin wallet private keys are not yet created. The 128 bits is still strong enough against any brute force attack.
